{"tid":444754,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好怕dead air","createTime":"2017-10-22T18:13:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-23T00:44:38.000Z","uid":102978,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"351eed3343a3a34eedec6b33e54fb776db1b0e1c","tid":444754,"uid":102978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T18:13:34.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇巴絲同我一樣<br />\n當同一個/以上既人身處同一個環境<br />\n唔講野會覺得好尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟著就會迫自己諗話題/搵啲野黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n特別係同鍾意既人一齊既時候...<br />\n如果唔講野我驚比人話悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b70b987bb16c5b39d5fbbf0e3db818c137eb38f","tid":444754,"uid":58583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T18:16:01.000Z","msg":"有個方程式可以唔dead<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc3eed871ef86aebdb032ac985ab53fb014b7e4f","tid":444754,"uid":54036,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T18:18:28.000Z","msg":"同感<br />\n但一出聲就做話題終結者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43faba212fa43d19d258e2de009d8049e1497398","tid":444754,"uid":55888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T18:23:04.000Z","msg":"冇話怕唔怕<br />\n不過我唔講野會死"},{"pid":"26d3b38ee768116721c933b6660db001372f6c05","tid":444754,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T18:51:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有個方程式可以唔dead<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n夾硬講仲辛苦過dead<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a088689ef6a48677d3851a30f4b67dea5528d9ac","tid":444754,"uid":72638,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T18:52:55.000Z","msg":"之前有巴打教過<br />\n睇多啲書報 多啲留意身邊既野<br />\n同人自然多話題"},{"pid":"9147456e2360eeb15c75b05c112e1000795b3ccf","tid":444754,"uid":102978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T23:17:00.000Z","msg":"其實我唔係冇野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係怕唔講野比人感覺悶同毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff633bd056ad192b8024b93109bc427132520c46","tid":444754,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T23:20:28.000Z","msg":"dead air好舒服啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9be88c95c0596bd990854b54ba4df32d94c8d18e","tid":444754,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T23:55:53.000Z","msg":"睇對方<br />\n唔想同你講野而dead air <br />\n唔講野都無所謂嘅dead air <br />\n<br />\n你會feel到有分別"},{"pid":"1bea8d903c96b5f5edf58b8772bda1d837a78be7","tid":444754,"uid":102978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T00:13:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇對方<br />\n唔想同你講野而dead air <br />\n唔講野都無所謂嘅dead air <br />\n<br />\n你會feel到有分別</blockquote><br />\n咁係唔講野都無所謂嘅dead air <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我鍾意果個女仔話過唔介意dead air<br />\n咁睇黎我唔應該迫自己係咁搵野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b9a53b6462b19ad51f6f44c8bff2ebe716080d4","tid":444754,"uid":92456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T00:39:21.000Z","msg":"如果一班人dead air會好怪<br />\n兩個人就睇對方, 多數親啲嘅人即使冇嘢講都可以好舒服(雖則好少)"},{"pid":"b9175a02ed810f1ad6b58b8d76a702a622a9eeda","tid":444754,"uid":37942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T00:44:38.000Z","msg":"你愈驚就愈Dead<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 